fm: void generate_permutation(vector<int> &num,       int index,       vector<int> &permutation,       vector<vector<int> > &results) {     int size = num.size();      if (size == index) {       results.push_back(permutation);     }     else {       for (int i = index; i < size; ++i) {         swap(num[index], num[i]);         permutation.push_back(num[index]);         generate_permutation(num, index + 1, permutation, results);         permutation.pop_back();         swap(num[index], num[i]);       }     }   }
